{"type": "article", "id": 14970, "title": "最火水桶包品牌开始卖女鞋，以及，阿迪达斯和日本潮牌推出联名系列 ｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2015-09-16T08:36:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 2881, "name": "Vera Wang"}, {"id": 16099, "name": "Badgley Mischka"}, {"id": 16100, "name": "Rodarte"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}, {"id": 16101, "name": "studio be-poles"}, {"id": 16102, "name": "Modernica"}, {"id": 2684, "name": "Mansur Gavriel"}, {"id": 2683, "name": "Esquire"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 9524, "name": "Kolor"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606003212srHpZwjDdIKqX3eW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些重要的新闻：<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>H&amp;M 8月销售仅增1%</strong>｜Hennes &amp; Mauritz AB 8 月份销售增幅骤降至 2013 年 3 月（下跌4%）以来的最低水平，亦结束了过去连续 10 个月的双位数增长。其最大单一市场德国、本土市场瑞典以及英国服装销售都十分疲软。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/prada-profits-10225235/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Prada 中期利润下跌 23% ，但决定提价</strong></a> ｜上半年 Prada SpA 普拉达集团净利润同比减少 23.0% 至 1.886 亿欧元，好过市场预料的 1.754 亿欧元，销售还是盈利均受到香港和澳门持续衰退的重大影响。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>英国 Vogue 要拍时尚纪录片 </strong>｜这个和英国 It Girl  Alexa Chung 一起拍摄的纪录片是一个系列，将会在 Vogue  视频频道上播放。纪录片将部分采用访谈的形式， Alexa Chung 将采访 Balmain 的 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/tag/olivier-rousteing/\">Olivier Rousteing</a> , <a href=\"http://wwd.com/tag/christopher-kane/\">Christopher Kane</a> 和 Sir <a href=\"http://wwd.com/tag/paul-smith-2/\">Paul Smith</a> 等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些值得一看的：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">纽约时装周第 6 天，这里是一些品牌的走秀。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tVera Wang 2016 年春夏成衣系列。<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003152E74zD1FZyv9SM2HV.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003152NPKpdZ9svzTWiOJL.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003153Y0HyCFzw97IO5iNV.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003153R4l8k6NhiuTVQDqZ.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003154O3e4xnyY1VogAL6r.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060031544NbaJk3hlWRp5wZj.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003155T6H8QJdeYaPKFm04.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003155RxTVnc45N7bC0QFP.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">Badgley Mischka 2016 年春夏成衣系列。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600315631bFTInRshCVBJgN.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003156yxzlbp3LB1T9jOK7.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003157CyeHzscpQ9Uwu2db.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060031578nEgUTdvfKZMsPtA.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003158wilLK3m1fuSFeqDN.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003158cOg4GFAo1KmCkuz7.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003159p2RmL5I7ED8jsMvb.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tRodarte 2016 年春夏成衣系列。<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003159EruzwVeZO6xW9XQF.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060032004rjasChn36HQ9x8d.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003200mcGBDo2XbQAeMTUg.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003201dYSbVrD2MHN9etm6.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003201Y0QoMNyhpvAwlKTS.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003202AoENLnBSp825Y6UR.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\tMarc Jacobs 的 DAISY 香水推出新套装。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003202TpnJCZObY5uoSxy6.jpg\" title=\"，，\" alt=\"，，\" data-ratio=\"0.60164512\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003203r6NOVSp9wIHygQMC.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.61253197\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t知名纹身艺术家 Dr. Woo 与 Modernica 推出的钢化玻璃椅，印上了脊椎的样子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003203qNKtwbjceBDfAsTh.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003203abhv7IWeczBKm5fC.jpg\" title=\"。。。\" alt=\"。。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003204F4gdoki3Jn9Qq6j7.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t卖包包的 Mansur Gavriel 发布了第一个女鞋系列。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003204xNelBXsz1mIKAWY9.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060032056MtYqWaJS9eEzfs0.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003205bvCfZou46lE3p915.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003206FiaoGQdleERrJ145.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<i>Esquire</i><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> 杂志选出了 80 年来 50 个最佳封面</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600320663g59Kz2du8LqYFa.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.3\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003207VR29DUz0gikGWFKS.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.31666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003207q0Gh7YoJklPgp4yS.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.32037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003208J0376uj1wAkOsM2o.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.3287037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003208NPUTVhL0rG4uanJg.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.29814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">Adidas 和日本潮牌 kolor 的联名秋冬系列，挺酷炫</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606060032090QhYCNyV65nDXF9Z.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003209LJAja2stREgbvToB.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003210Dt3m1YWnN5GIiFMz.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003210n8IucarRQ0JMLvX2.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003211bzS0tnMWoplZVqC3.jpg\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t一些有意思的说法：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tKate Spade 在向 Apple 和 Lululemon 学习，它把自己的销售人员叫“缪斯”。Lululemon 管店里的销售叫 Educators，而 Apple 你也知道 Geniuses，至于宜家和星巴克，他们都叫 Partner。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}